rComments: Anjan was incredible, one of the best teachers I've had! It is shame that he had to leave the IHPST...

Anjan provides excellent feedback, is easy to talk to and provides insightful reflections on the material. If you enjoy analytical philosophy, he is the professor for you. If you don?t, his courses are still worth while.
Everybody loves Anjan! I've taken 8 courses at IHPST and he is THE BEST! His lectures are extremely dense but helpful.
Prof. C was awesome. He was totally smart and helpful. Tough class, but wicked prof.
Anjan is sooooooo hotttt! He gets 6 chili peppers from over here! Oh, and he's a good prof.

Definitely a great professor! Material is mind blowing but he does an excellent job of putting it all into perspective such that you don't lose interest in "everyone's" fav topic, metaphysics. Course is not easy but worth taking.
Amazing Prof.!!!  It was a hard class, but Prof. C was VERY helpful, always VERY clear, and a pleasure to listen to for the whole lecture.  An amazing voice or tone, whatever it was, he's GREAT!
